    <p>Your MP3 files will only be used to suggest metadata to you. We will not store your MP3s unless you want to access the preview feature. We will not use your files for training or generation of any models.</p> -->
    <h2>What Cuemonic is not</h2>
    <p>
      Cuemonic is not a DAW. It does not store your project files, and it does
      not help you write music.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cuemonic is not a music library app. It does not play your cues (except
      for a preview if you choose), and it does not help you manage your music
      files.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cuemonic is not a music publishing platform. It does not help you find
      publishers, and it does not help you manage your publishing contracts.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cuemonic is not a music licensing platform. It does not help you license
      your music, and it does not help you manage your licensing agreements.
    </p>
    <p class="pull">
      Cuemonic is a tool to help you manage your cue metadata. It is designed to
      be simple, easy to use, and <em>focused</em> on solving the metadata problem
      for production composers.
    </p>
