    <p class="pull">Ready to give it a try?</p>
    <p>
      Check out Cuemonic free for 14 days. <a href="https://tally.so/r/3E29Ar"
        >Sign up for our beta now!</a>
    </p>
    <h3>What to expect?</h3>
    <p>
      We are ramping up slowly to ensure a smooth experience. We will email you
      a link to subscribe when we are ready for the next set of composers.
    </p>
  </div>
</Page>
